## README
Just a simple package for solving constrained optimization problems using the Frank-Wolfe or Conditional Gradient algorithm.

In the folder frank_wolfe you will find the main methods of the package.

algorithms -> contains various implementations of different Frank-Wolfe variants, e.g., base (vanilla) Frank-Wolfe, away-step Frank-Wolfe, boosted Frank-Wolfe, mistmatched Frank-Wolfe, Nonconvex Nonsmooth Frank-Wolfe, and conditional sliding.
core -> contains many core functions, like the Linear Minimization Oracle for many sets (lmo.py) and some utilities (objective function class, utility functions in util.py)

In the folder examples you can see implementations of these algorithms on some simple examples in jupyter notebooks.
